devdoc.title: Maintains a sorted list of unsigned ints keyed by uint256.

contains(SortedLinkedList.List storage,u.notice: Returns whether or not a particular key is present in the sorted list.

getElements(SortedLinkedList.List storag.notice: Gets all elements from the doubly linked list.

getValue(SortedLinkedList.List storage,u.notice: Returns the value for a particular key in the sorted list.

insert(SortedLinkedList.List storage,uin.notice: Inserts an element into a doubly linked list.

popN(SortedLinkedList.List storage,uint2.notice: Removes N elements from the head of the list and returns their keys.

push(SortedLinkedList.List storage,uint2.notice: Inserts an element at the end of the doubly linked list.

remove(SortedLinkedList.List storage,uin.notice: Removes an element from the doubly linked list.

update(SortedLinkedList.List storage,uin.notice: Updates an element in the list.
